<tr><td class="printline">
<span class="postbody">ya its not 20% minus 10%
<br />
its 20% minus (10% of 20%) so 20 minus 2 for level 68 and 20 minus 4 for level 69 and so on.
<br />

<br />
btw the skirt rocks, no more robe look! yah!</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
